Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.01,0:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,40)}第180话 红色杀意的夜想曲(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.93,0:00:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的風找不到蹤蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取決於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國來的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴調音 暗藏殺意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.14,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.69,0:01:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色殺意的夜想曲(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.54,0:01:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加那娛樂集團可是個大公司啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長先生有什麽事情麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.84,0:02:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的公司要出版傑拉爾天馬的CD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.45,0:02:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備開一個簽約和慶祝的晚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬終於到日本來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國流行樂壇現在最紅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的日本歌手 我當然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於他過去的經曆誰也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從晚會的日期定下之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.74,0:02:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子美咲的週圍就怪事不斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多次電話沒人講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有寫發送人的玫瑰花束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視我的愛的人會下地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一封是昨天寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複仇的宴會馬上就要開幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受恐怖的晚會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚會是三天以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也不能取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我很爲妻子擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有什麽懷疑對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的簽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是秘密進行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚會的知情者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們夫婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那四個準備出蓆晚會的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抛棄了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我至今無法忘記你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠關註著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興的發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是天馬的紅色愛的夜想曲的日文歌詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天給你獻上一朵花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金盞花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.25,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半邊蓮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大紅的大理花以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情的曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這歌詞哪裏好  蘭這傢夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能夠見到天馬 太倖福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可是去幹活的 幹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.24,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是會長的朋友毛利田一傢 記住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓人知道我是個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 看不出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.65,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都註意點舉止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我該說的話哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 從入口到門前還要開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像外國電影一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真豪華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大富豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽有點像恐怖電影裏面的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇人打雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還是晴天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想見傑拉爾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕和這沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毛利田先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我就是受到邀請的毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.03,0:05:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正等你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的秘書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫德大寺昌代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是會場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術品都很出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我妻子的收藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請這邊坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能先參觀一下你的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德大寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他們去參觀一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.23,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我妻子美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任集團公司加那音樂出版社社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽我們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌代去廚房幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人好像討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是大廳的正上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息室的最裏面是鋼琴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是大富豪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室內還有回廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會碰壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是裝飾品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料和制作方法都和真的沒有區別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是真的麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴室的隔壁是我的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間也很有品位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們夫婦的結婚照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在斐濟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.04,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大學時代就是同一個音樂小組的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往了一年就結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無比羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.93,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.13,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情經常發生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一個沙啞的男人聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕聲低語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我接 他立刻就掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麽懷疑對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不僅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有和信一起寄來的這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你不知情的時候拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天早上和金盞花一起放在門廊上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是昨天照的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是覺得有人在看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰的下一個是金盞花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是被人註視著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以毛利小五郎的名譽保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡力保護美咲女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人們到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.83,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是傑拉爾天馬的經紀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是米歇爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我哥哥加那善則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他的妻子美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.96,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 他還有事 遲到三十分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 那邊那位是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的舊友毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的小孩蘭和柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田 這是我弟弟秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任加那音樂出版社的副社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢請這邊坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著就好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幹什麽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽帶外人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾的契約 現在可是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你任性的去了法國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張的把傑拉爾帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爲了公司才這樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你批評我毫無道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.64,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麽做 你在美咲面前就不能露臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.95,0:11:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想方設法要和美咲親近嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.56,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你和德大寺又是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個公司都傳遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻話 我和她之間沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.73,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我一定要簽了約給你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.65,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾差不多該到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去門廊等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去一趟衛生間再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上下一道菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田的酒也喝完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失陪一下 去補妝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.35,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲沒人陪著沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.96,0:12:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 幹活 幹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女化妝室我怎麽進得去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被雷擊了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不對頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.04,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.25,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門鎖著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪裏去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.25,0:13:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是誰關了電閘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.19,0:13:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麽事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是誰突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.60,0:14:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半邊蓮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個果然還是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 那首歌裏也有這個花名的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.05,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色愛的夜想曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玫瑰 金盞花和半邊蓮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是犯人至今送來的花嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.29,0:14:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠關註著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興的發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.73,0:14:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽按照傑拉爾天馬的歌詞在騷擾美咲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騷擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.34,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽人故意在騷擾美麗的夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.74,0:14:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位 非常抱歉 晚會開到一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我問幾個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把電閘拉起來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我趕過來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把樓梯旁邊的電閘拉起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹當時在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田 你是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我不是毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有名的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你鎖上的門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我正要補妝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈突然滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人從後面襲擊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看見犯人的臉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的不是十分清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披著披風 面無表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外國人的容貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 爲什麽看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.83,0:15:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時你在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了迎接傑拉爾 我去了門廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽到救命的喊聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人就到這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾是我們重要的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.89,0:16:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是今天的主角 傑拉爾天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樓沒有人 所以我就上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛出了一點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們下樓談談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢也都下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門上了鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時犯人已經在房間裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前離開大廳的所有人都有作案時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電閘是誰拉斷的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人不止一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.54,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽東西的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷口還是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些小塊的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是神秘東西留下的痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當時 各位都在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一停電我就著急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.89,0:17:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在廚房看著夫人烤的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多都淋濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大門那裏下的計程車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢先休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧糕 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.56,0:17:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子又不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.83,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能去我的房間給我把藥拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的照片拍的就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生過激烈的打鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲和傑拉爾天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是美咲結婚之前半年嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸又要說你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 不行 蘭 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前和美咲有什麽關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 太沒禮貌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹 你事先就知道 故意的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽這麽說我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.94,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你結婚之前我確實和這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原名叫天馬純也得人戀愛過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他是個默默無聞的音樂傢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是十年前的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.15,0:19:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.46,0:19:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了傑拉爾天馬的資料大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上怎麽有這麽巧的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.03,0:19:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 這是給你帶的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我傢裏手工制作的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本是買不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 就請允許我先嘗嘗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有什麽問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們喝果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位請過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起幹杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然還是有戒備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我還烤著蛋糕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌代 你去地下室把那套銀茶具拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位嘗嘗我特制的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.40,0:20:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作爲讓你的公司出版夜想曲的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想稍加改動 重新制作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新制作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾本人強烈要求這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這花是在門廊找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.16,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大理花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花語是背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大傢久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢都不要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬 能不能給我們唱幾首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易請到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你襲擊美咲的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你還有誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要準備一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃跑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡攪蠻纏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麽事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.85,0:22:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.66,0:22:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.05,0:23:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色愛的夜想曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.46,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌是十年前天馬送給美咲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.23,0:24:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是血麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.31,0:24:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是襲擊美咲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.34,0:24:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.64,0:24:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色殺意的夜想曲(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.35,0:24:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.95,0:24:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.75,0:24:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集揭開謎底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.65,0:24:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘀嘀嘀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.75,0:24:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.86,0:24:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結案的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.96,0:24:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.96,0:00:24.83,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}正因你我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.85,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}喜好各異 腳程與表達方式也大異其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.60,0:00:40.77,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}如今的我們 在對方的記憶中 正漸漸褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.56,0:00:48.27,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}我摸索過 卻開始尋找 其他人 的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.35,0:00:55.41,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}我比想象中活得更堅強 去追求 特別的 愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.53,0:00:59.37,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}苦惱著　難以應付的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.66,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-1.4}true heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.79,0:01:10.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}爲了不會再度迷失 那只手 我絕不松開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.43,0:01:13.05,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}即使是彼此受傷的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.18,0:01:24.56,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}我只是 一直在這個 迷惘的時空中 搜尋著答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.81,0:01:31.03,Opening,NTP,0000,0316,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}{\fad(0,1000)}到下個地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.81,0:01:31.03,Opening,NTP,0000,-0111,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-1.4}{\fad(0,1000)}you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.40,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}{\fad(0,1000)}請抱緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.53,0:01:42.58,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-1.4}{\fad(0,1000)}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.96,0:22:40.21,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}不知道　該用什麽話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.63,0:22:47.30,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}才能　告訴你我真正的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.39,0:22:56.60,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}從那時起　不知過了多少季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.27,0:23:02.52,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}雖然時間無情地流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.32,0:23:10.07,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}你卻總是　微笑地陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.99,0:23:20.34,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}我沒對你說出口的 至今 還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.30,Ending,NTP,0000,0225,0000,,{\be1\fsp-1.8}Secret of my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.30,Ending,NTP,0000,-0230,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}請你不要懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.42,0:23:31.43,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}無論何時　只要還有少許未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.43,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}真相　是緊握在手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.11,Ending,NTP,0000,0448,0000,,{\be1\fsp-1.8}{\fscx130}I can't say
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.11,Ending,NTP,0000,0180,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}請給我點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.11,Ending,NTP,0000,-0231,0000,,{\be1\fsp-1.8}{\fscx130}I'm waiting for a chance
